# AtlasLab - sshd_config for the atlaslab/switch image.
# Same rationale as docker/frr-atlaslab/sshd_config: no UsePAM directive
# (this sshd build has no PAM support - the keyword itself is rejected,
# not just the PAM behavior), host keys generated fresh at container
# startup rather than baked into the image.

Port 22
AddressFamily inet

PasswordAuthentication yes
PubkeyAuthentication yes
PermitEmptyPasswords no
ChallengeResponseAuthentication no
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no

PermitRootLogin no
AllowUsers atlas

StrictModes no
LogLevel INFO

Subsystem sftp internal-sftp
